desc_short	-----								Sketch Tales is D.R.A.W.I.N.G. Sandbox – or Doodling Roleplay Action With Imaginative Nonlinear Gameplay. Need a sword? Draw it. Need company? Sketch a creature and it will come to life. You have the power to save this world or to create your own one.							
